><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Education Qualification</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Graduates or relevant degree</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Age Limit</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">20 years to 28 years</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><font style=\"\" color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">RBI Assistant Salary</span></font></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Rs. 45,050/-</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">RBI Official Website</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">www.rbi.org.in</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><div id=\"incontent-middle\" style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 5px;\"><center></center><center></center></div></div><h2 id=\"YFJNHDT407ASCPD48M5SS9IQTEQGP3DC\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Assistant Recruitment - Important Dates&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Assistant Notification&nbsp; with a complete schedule will be released on the official website. All important dates for the RBI Assistant&nbsp; exam will be updated in the table below as soon as the dates are announced with the RBI Assistant Recruitment Notification pdf.&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">RBI Assistant Recruitment - Important Dates&nbsp;</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Activity</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Date</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">RBI Assistant Notification&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">January&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">RBI Assistant Apply Online Start Date</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">January&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Online Application Form Last Date</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">February&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Last Date to Pay Fees</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">February&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">RBI Assistant Preliminary Exam Date&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">RBI Assistant Mains Exam Date&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">--</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"JR5AHGMKO7LUJOLM01ERYI57MNPGGH8T\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Assistant Vacancy&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Assistant Vacancy will be announced along with RBI Assistant Notification . As expected, the vacancies can be around 540.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Last year RBI had introduced 450 vacancies for Assistant posts</span>. The category-wise &amp; state-wise vacancy distribution has been updated below for RBI Assistant 2023.</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222,