lor: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Govt Jobs</span></font></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 218.387px;\">Exam Type</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 672.812px;\">National Level</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 218.387px;\">Eligibility</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 672.812px;\">Graduate (bachelor’s degree in relevant discipline)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Age Limit</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">18 to 32 Years</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 218.387px;\">Selection Process</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 672.812px;\"><ul style=\"padding-left: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><li>Tier 1 (Qualifying)</li><li>Tier 2</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Salary</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Varies posts wise (Pay Level 4 to 7)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 218.387px;\">Official Website</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; width: 672.812px;\">www.ssc.gov.in</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"JPP364O7CGIYWG2LAKMOAUN0AGGN63QC\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">SSC CGL Recruitment Important Dates</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-weight: bolder;\">The Staff Selection Commission has announced the notification and exam month along with&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">SSC Calendar&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-weight: bolder;\">.</span><font color=\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">&nbsp;</font><font style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Check important dates regarding the SSC CGL exam from the table below.&nbsp;</font></p><figure class=\"table\" sty