t year,<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;14582 vacancies will be filled this year</span>. The post-wise and category-wise vacancies for SSC CGL 2025 can be checked from here.&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px; width: 267.288px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Posts</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px; width: 341.837px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Department</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px; width: 58.8125px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Total</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px; width: 57.05px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">UR</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px; width: 55.3125px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">SC</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0