Sikkim</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Gangtok, Bardang City</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Tamilnadu</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Chennai, Vellore, Coimbatore, Erode, Thirupur, Madurai, Virudhunagar, Dindigul Salem, Namakkal, Thiruchirapalli, Perambalur, Pudukottai, Thanjavur, Tirunelvelli, Kanyakumari, Tuticorin</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Tripura</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Agartala</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Uttar Pradesh</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Agra, Allahabad, Bareilly, Gorakhpur, Kanpur, Lucknow, Meerut, Varanasi</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Uttarakhand</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Dehradun, Haldwani, Nainital, Roorkee City</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">West Bengal</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Berhampore (WB), Durgapur, Kolkata, Greater Kolkata, Howrah, Hooghly, Kalyani, Siliguri</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><br><h2 id=\"VCNTRCXH2MR5DKCUEN1X04YRNUR8NTG2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Grade B&nbsp; Admit Card</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The officials will be issuing RBI Grade B Admit Cards to the candidates whose applications are submitted successfully. The admit cards for each phase will be released separately and have to be downloaded from the official website www.rbi.org.in using the registration number and password.</p><h2 id=\"SKCN9789LIA3HDQRKU4AMKBP5QEXJDX3\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Grade B Result</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The results for the RBI Grade B&nbsp; Exam will be released after the completion of each phase of the exam. A candidate is required to qualify for both Phase I and Phase II exams to get a chance to sit for the interview process. The merit list is prepared in descending order of the marks obtained by candidates after the interview process is complete. The final selection is based on how well you do in your interview.</p><h2 id=\"E9NBHLWJLN38S5MAEUYB9SMYRD7JMUJN\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">RBI Grade B&nbsp; Cut Off</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The cut-off for the RBI Grade B&nbsp; Exam will be released after each phase of the examination is completed. The cut-off for the Phase-I exam will be released first, followed by the cut-off for the Phase-II exam. Candidates can evaluate their marks and chances of selection by matching their score with the cut-off list released by RBI. Check last year\'s RBI Grade B Exam Cut-Off for reference.</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"6\" style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">RBI Grade-B Cut-Off 2025 for Phase-I Exam&nbsp;</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Section&nbsp;</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">General/UR&nbsp;</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">EWS&nbsp;</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">OBC</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">SC</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">ST&nbsp;</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">General Awareness</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">24</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">16</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">20</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">16</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">16</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">English Language</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">9</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">6</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">7.50</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">6</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">6</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Quantitative Aptitude</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">9</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">6</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">7.50</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">6</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">6</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Reasoning</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">18</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">12</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">15</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">12</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">12</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Total Score Aggregate</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">77.50</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">64.75</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">69</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">65</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">64.75</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>', 0, '2026-01-29 09:59:04', '2026-02-18 07:36:45');
INSERT INTO `bank_po_exam_tabs` (`id`, `exam_id`, `tab_title`, `tab_content`, `display_order`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(93, 17, 'HOME', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">Every year, the Institute of Banking Personnel Selection (IBPS) invites banking aspirants who are willing to apply for the post of Probationary Officer (PO), Officer Scale 2 &amp; 3, and Office Assistants (Clerks) in the participating Regional Rural Banks (RRBs) across the country. Lakhs of banking aspirants are waiting for the IBPS RRB Recruitment&nbsp; (क्षेत्रीय ग्रामीण बैंक). The selection is made for the following posts:&nbsp;</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Posts Under IBPS RRB</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Office Assistant (Clerk)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Marketing Manager</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Treasury Manager</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Officer Scale – I (PO)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Banking Officer Scale - II</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Agriculture Officer (Grade – II)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Law Officer (Grade – II)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Law Officer (Grade – II)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Chartered Accountant (Grade II)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Officer (Grade III)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">IT Officer (Grade II)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">For selection to the posts of both Assistant and Officer Cadre in Regional Rural Banks (RRBs), IBPS organises the IBPS RRB Exam every year. IBPS RRB is a national-level banking exam conducted by the Institute of Banking Personnel Selection (IBPS) for candidates who aspire to join the Regional Rural Bank (क्षेत्रीय ग्रामीण बैंक). Let’s take a look at both of these exams.</p><br><h2 id=\"EP6W1TFBPRYXILMRQS27KXQ4DPPRDXWH\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">IBPS RRB&nbsp; Exam Highlights</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The official advertisement for IBPS RRB recruitment&nbsp; (CRP RRBs XV) will be published officially for PO, Clerk, and Officer Scale 2 &amp; 3 posts to be filled for 28 Participating Banks. For more details about IBPS RRB , go through the table below.</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><