: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Category</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Fee</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">SC/ST/PWBD</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">175</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Other Category</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">850</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"P5UHF7L86AKHD85FAVCH537JD0K1QJVM\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">IBPS RRB&nbsp; Online Application Form</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The Online Application link for IBPS RRB&nbsp; Office Assistant and Officers Scale-I, II &amp; III will be activated after the release of the official notification at the official website, i.e. https://ibps.in. All candidates can check all the important details regarding IBPS RRB Apply Online&nbsp; by clicking on the link mentioned below:</p><br><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"></figure><h2 id=\"PBJK5NI3C1MNL2670QKV90NJ1KOKVNKX\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">IBPS RRB Salary Structure<br></h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">IBPS RRB Salary</span>&nbsp;varies for the posts released. IBPS RRB officers receive their salary as per the latest revised pay commission and the approximate monthly salary has been tabulated below-&nbsp;</span></p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Post Name</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Monthly Income</span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Officer Scale-I</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Rs. 60,000 to Rs. 61,000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Officer Scale-II</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Rs. 75,000 to Rs. 77,000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Officer Scale-III</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Rs 80,000 to Rs 90,000</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Office Assistant (Multipurpose)</td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(64, 64, 64); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px;\">Rs. 35,000 to Rs. 37,000</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"DWNDS2S2AO37BD48F2MKNXQ9DPEI6KIC\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 28px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline-block; width: 892px; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">IBPS RRB&nbsp; Participating Banks</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); text-align: justify; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The banking aspirants interested in the vacancies of IBPS RRB Office Assistant, Officer Scale I, II, and III must be keen to know which banks have been added to the list. In this article, we have listed all 28 Participating Regional Rural Banks.</p><figure class=\"table\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; --bs-table-bg: transparent; --bs-table-striped-color: #212529; --bs-table-striped-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); --bs-table-active-color: #212529; --bs-table-active-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); --bs-table-hover-color: #212529; --bs-table-hover-bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075); width: 892px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); border-color: rgb(222, 226, 230); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><table style=\"width: 892px;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; background: rgba(49, 43, 71, 0.05); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Sr. No.</span></td><td style=\"border-color: rgb(99, 97, 107); padding-right: 5px; padding-lef